        span.content__item-header-meta JBY
        h2.content__item-header-title JUST BE YOURSELF
      .content__item-copy
        p.content__item-copy-text
          | Stephen listened in scornful silence. She bows her old head to a voice
          | that speaks to her loudly, her bonesetter, her medicineman: me she
          | slights. To the voice that will shrive and oil for the grave all there
          | is of her but her woman&rsquo;s unclean loins, of man&rsquo;s flesh made not in
          | God&rsquo;s likeness, the serpent&rsquo;s prey.
        a.content__item-copy-more(href='#') project +
